WPScan is a command-line security scanner used to identify known vulnerabilities in WordPress core, themes, and plugins,It relies on an up-to-date vulnerability database maintained by the WPScan team.

Usage :
wpscan --url https://yourwebsite.com -e vp --api-token YOUR_TOKEN
wpscan --url https://yourwebsite.com -e vt --api-token YOUR_TOKEN

-e vp â†’ Vulnerable plugins only
-e vt â†’ Vulnerable themes only


                                                                                    
